# Screenshots

> Placeholder directory for app screenshots, store assets, and demo GIFs.

When the first UI milestone lands, this directory will hold:

- `watch-live.png` — live battery card on the watch
- `watch-history.png` — RDB history view on the watch
- `phone-24h.png` — 24h drain curve on the phone
- `phone-7d.png` — 7d aggregated curve
- `demo.gif` — end-to-end demo recording

Until then, this `.gitkeep` is here so the directory exists in version control.
